Terminator :
 Install : apt install terminator
1) Toggle fulscreen : F11
2) Split terminals horizontally : Ctrl + Shift + O
3) Split terminals vertically   : Ctrl + Shift + E
4) Move to terminal above the current one : Alt + <UpArrow>
5) Move to terminal below the current one : Alt + <DownArrow>
6) Move to terminal left of current one   : Alt + <LeftArrow>
7) Move to terminal right of current one  : Alt + <RightArrow>
8) Freeze running command                 : Ctrl + s
9) Resume the command                     : Ctrl + q
10) Kill running command                  : Ctrl + c

